{"title":"绮","date":"2020-01-07T01:13:17.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 7, 2020","L":"01/07/2020","MM-DD":"01-07"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2020/01/07/nyzkUTQlq8be4YP.jpg","link":"2020/01/07/绮","comments":true,"tags":["他","梦"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-02-10T17:01:29.420Z","content":"<p>五色的蝴蝶在丛中飞舞<br>交错的巨大的巨颈<br>遮掩在盖大的叶片下<br>走入从中不觉惊慌  </p>\n<p>尽头是红褐色的岩石<br>转身水已没过<br>绿色的茎叶格外鲜嫩  </p>\n<p>纵身跳进湖中<br>双臂充满活力<br>跃出水面<br>旋即又回岩岸边  </p>\n<p>轻快地在崎岖中穿梭<br>闪耀的碎片零落殆尽<br>睁开眼<br>窗前的人，窗外的雪  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>2020.01.07</em><br><em>北京</em> </p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"Promises第二章","link":"2020/01/09/PromisesChapter2"},"next":{"title":"Promises第一章","link":"2020/01/06/PromisesChapter1"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/01/07/绮/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"February 11, 2020"}}